    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a speck of dust or a single scratch on it. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin. You won't be disappointed!",
