    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its original luster. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip, while the interior still carries that unmistakable 'new car' scent. Every surface\u2014from the supple, uncreased leather upholstery to the high-gloss trim\u2014is absolutely flawless. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting its pampered life. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality. All systems function perfectly, and the ride is whisper-quiet and incredibly tight. If you are looking for the absolute best, you have found it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
