      "description": "Presenting a masterfully preserved vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its class. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity and operates with the precision of a showroom-fresh unit. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
